Company Overview of MAST Capital Management, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
MAST Capital Management, LLC is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. It provides its services to private investment funds and registered investment companies. The firm launches and manages hedge funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. MAST Capital Management, LLC was formed in May 2002 and is based in Boston, Massachusetts.


